{"tid":1888280,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"余海峰：用垃圾形容陳雲，係對垃圾既侮辱","createTime":"2020-02-20T06:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T08:49:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"840412f6aeee5e3d6d5a940576efc80025286d7a","tid":1888280,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QptY3Zt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQptY3Zt.png&h=40cede3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48716ffdfecbf5fc31bf7839d7275167097c743","tid":1888280,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:08:02.000Z","msg":"陳雲會唔會變成下一個奧姆真理教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca6e56a486ba446daea5b989cd4e165ac65753a","tid":1888280,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"即使被當作罪人而死，並且遭受輕藐，只要能因此創造眾多生命的未來，我就沒什麼好害怕的！燃燒吧，我的小宇宙，成為照亮未來的希望之光！"},{"pid":"95d71f0a7395e09a390f9288ca3ada47b6ccd5af","tid":1888280,"uid":269061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:14:04.000Z","msg":"這膠戲我不演了！<br />\n<br />\n中共的 WARS 大概是混合了多種病毒，中共國湖北的是高毒性版本，傳播出去的是低毒性版本。<br />\n<br />\n整艘鑽石公主號，幾百人確診，只得幾個老人病情嚴重，七十人毫無病徵，威力與所謂的瘟疫差很遠。船上隔離是多餘的，一早就都染了 WARS，但染病的未必發病，發病的多數輕微。<br />\n<br />\n日本要忙奧運，不想玩這政治瘟疫。反正只是美共冷戰的小插曲，原本是中共以此賴皮不履行貿然協議，但美國表明不准中共賴賬，政治劇爛尾收場。現在中共只在考慮要用 BBQ 還是要打邊爐作結。反正結果一樣，日本索性趕走所有不幸的參與者，算是人道了。<br />\n<br />\n（不要以為香港沒有爆發是因為各位有口罩。過百萬人於新年往返中共國卻不足一百人確診，就足夠顯示病毒的威力弱。若對所有過境人士檢驗，相信會發現有極多人感染，只是他們病徵太弱，現在沒有找出來。社區感染可能早就發生，只是染病的沒發病而已。）<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%97%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A8%B1%E9%9A%B1%E5%BD%A2%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%82%B3%E6%9F%93%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E4%BD%8E-%E4%BD%8F%E9%99%A2%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E7%B8%AE%E7%9F%AD%E8%87%B3%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5-208077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%259A%25B1%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%259F%2593%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%25E4%25BD%258E-%25E4%25BD%258F%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E7%259F%25AD%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2597%25A5-208077&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=dcc91dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%97%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A8%B1%E9%9A%B1%E5%BD%A2%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%82%B3%E6%9F%93%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E4%BD%8E-%E4%BD%8F%E9%99%A2%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E7%B8%AE%E7%9F%AD%E8%87%B3%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5-208077</a><br />\n<br />\n陳雲下線：敗屙嘥仁時"},{"pid":"47a427c2723000345fff698001eb68b1e82939c0","tid":1888280,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a48716ffdfecbf5fc31bf7839d7275167097c743","tid":1888280,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:08:02.000Z","msg":"陳雲會唔會變成下一個奧姆真理教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:49:32.000Z","msg":"喂，而家冇人識㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}